Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.10,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.64,0:01:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.36,0:01:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了打倒支配遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們以第七星界為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了拯救被多壞達支配了的宇宙界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從第三星界來到迪瑪星的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在大都會市得知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,圓球不倒翁製造地上戰艦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們雖然幫助市內的機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去收拾地上戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但這時喜歡改造機械人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,維修員的魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.66,0:02:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡粉碎機卻出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打倒了死亡粉碎機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得到機械人們的力量也成功破壞了地上戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心想火美子也平安回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次卻是真正的布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被圓球不倒翁捉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯,正因如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.30,0:02:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.51,0:02:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二十話\N飛馳吧 太空手推礦車!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於駕臨了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尊敬的布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無禮者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要用那可怕的熱情臉孔接近公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快退開…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以把那封印了星力的鑰匙交給我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起,我不知道什麼鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.66,0:03:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,你怎樣也說不知道的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只有用一點強硬的手段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來,這是公主最討厭的蕎頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚼嚼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要!不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你對公主幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚼嚼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已無路可退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚼嚼嚼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了,封印星力的鑰匙是藏在某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.81,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鑰匙在迪瑪星的象徵,太陽塔內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太陽塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎?原來是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大臣,說謊是皇室成員的羞恥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主,說謊是一種方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在要爭到時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等救世主來救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無禮者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以為這位大人物是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這位便是迪瑪星的布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布…布莉布莉公主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你便是他們要找的布莉布莉公主嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的和火美子一模一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無禮者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的一點也不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.77,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主,沒時間和這沒貴氣的家夥混下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要盡快把我們的位置通知救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒貴氣真對不起呢,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…很痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.47,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是大臣,這裏沒有電話也沒有郵局啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方法是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由這家夥通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大臣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我絕不能留下公主一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼要怎樣做啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留下公主一個人是絕不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大臣,我自己一個人沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這裏等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣便和把星力得到手一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟著只剩下把渡收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,角畢迪,之後拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已…已走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡和大叔也真沒用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去…去太陽塔,快點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牛牛丸出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼只要乘搭那太空火車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便能先他們一步到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.77,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼,圓球不倒翁他們窺伺的星力到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是支持著迪瑪星的巨大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就和我之前說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙界因為有迪瑪星在中心才能得以平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,圓球不倒翁是想窺伺那星力而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主便把星力封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶著鑰匙去到第三星界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.28,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也因此迪瑪星便開始遠離了宇宙界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙界的眾星也面臨著被滅的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬一星力被用在魔神身上的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便會變成了星界山最強的魔神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此這件事是個秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.49,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來龍神丸的威力增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是全靠星力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解開星力的鑰匙在公主身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要在圓球不倒翁拿到手之前救出她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,趕快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了,牛仔去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,動不了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,自從迪瑪星散開以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,軌道變得亂七八糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不是能行走的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轟隆轟隆GOGO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.79,0:08:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趕快趕快,要再加快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等,會不會太快了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,還未夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果公主有什麼閃失的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然如此,但真的太快了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超速了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以呢…剎車制…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!?什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,有些字寫著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界文我看不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剎車制故障中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你平安的和渡先生他們會合了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在只能寄望如此了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話怎樣也要盡量拖延這東西到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,絲帶鬆脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請幫我縛回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.69,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這點小事自己來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遲早會在某處脫軌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算你這樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果有電話的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便能叫戰神丸來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.16,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.17,0:10:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是忍部一族代代相傳的傳信鴿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戰神丸,你來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戰神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.24,0:11:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣渡他們便會飛出宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.48,0:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定會得到很大的獎勵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過山車,過山車!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好,布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也好,打爛它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是做得很好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點也不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那便是太陽塔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,只差一點罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是圓球不倒翁的要塞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已追上了,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.04,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡的渡,今次一定送你下地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,離開了太陽塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前面是燒得紅紅的火炎地獄溶礦爐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次一定是你的死期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接近熔爐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變得熱起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,叫龍神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,危險!趴下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了,叫不了龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去的話會飛進熔爐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以從那裏跳出去,呼喚龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,萬一踏錯一步便會沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,你忘記了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是救世主渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們溶掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.69,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要趕快接住推礦車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.34,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡第一,渡超了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的,真危險呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟不斷暗地裏使出卑鄙手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,堂堂正正決一勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙飛腿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙重拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.65,0:17:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這便是我本人的堂堂正正的戰鬥方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會輸,我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.48,0:17:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,繁星的能量在我的體內燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍星力量!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變身,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變了身也是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看招,高明導彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,可以用新的招式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名字叫銀河龍彈拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,銀河龍彈拳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,銀河龍彈拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算什麼,象徵力量!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,動不了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.90,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我把你那大面孔打歪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那部魔神是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來不是多壞達的手下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但阻礙的人不可以饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,銀河龍牙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.78,0:19:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡,你記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閣下是古利古利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古利古利王子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初次見面,我是古利古利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是從宇宙界邊緣中的一顆小行星來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很多謝你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,這是理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了,我一直在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是火美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火-美-子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然很相似,但她不是布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.36,0:21:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古利古利王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.56,0:21:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主被圓球不倒翁捉去太陽塔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們在幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為你是公主便大意起來,我真蠢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.25,0:21:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布莉布莉公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已到了太陽塔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.21,0:21:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封印了星力的鑰匙在哪裏?
